Worcester.Millbury Street Head Start: The Millbury Street Head Start is a historic building providing Head Start programs within the Worcester Public Schools. Located on Millbury Street in Worcester, Massachusetts, the building was originally used as the Millbury Street Schoolhouse #4 and later known as the Ward Street School. The 2-1/2 story brick Romanesque building was designed by J. W. Patston and built in 1898-99.
